            <td style="padding: 12px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #ddd; background: #E8F5E9;"><strong>0%</strong> anytime</td>
          </tr>
          <tr style="background: #F5F0E8;">
            <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><strong>Approval Speed</strong></td>
