        <li><strong>March:</strong> Last chance for some tax year-ends</li>
        <li><strong>April-June:</strong> Good for H2 equipment needs</li>
        <li><strong>July-September:</strong> Plan for year-end projects</li>
        <li><strong>October-November:</strong> Pre-year-end purchases</li>
        <li><strong>December:</strong> Final chance for 2026 deductions</li>
